Docs HTML sprecial chars





https://mailtrap.io/blog/nbsp/


Name	                                    HTML Entity	  Entity Number
Non-breaking space	                      &nbsp;	 
Less than (<)	                            &lt;	        <
More than (>)	                            &gt;	        >
Ampersand (&)	                            &amp;	        &
Euro (€)	                                &euro;	      €
Pound (£)	                                &pound;	      £
double quotation mark (“)	                &quot;	      “
single quotation mark (apostrophe) (‘)	  &apos;	      ‘






